Company Profile:Art Of Click is a niche Premium Mobile Ad Network / Media Agency, operating primarily in South East Asia. We offer mainly Performance-based campaigns to brands, agencies and content providers. Our models include CPC, CPA, CPD, CPI, CPL, in short all mechanisms behind the click.
Job Description:Art Of Click is looking for an analytical, eager and driven individual to undertake a 4 to 12 month internship in our Sales team in Singapore. This is an excellent opportunity for someone to build a working knowledge of projects and client engagement within a mobile advertising start up in Singapore. Reporting to the CEO, the Sales Intern supports the company with the execution of all sales activities.   The Sales  Intern will help to grow Company’s sales and client utilization using the latest demand generation tools.·   Building client/prospect relationship management database:Researching on LinkedIn, GooglePlay, AppStore, other sites, existing prospect contacts to obtain useful relationship information that will help in targeting new leadsEnsure proper prospect management in SalesForce.comHelp to email / contact / follow up the prospects·   Competitor Intelligence:·       Support global website and conducting own analysis using secondary and primary sources.·       Share relevant knowledge with sales teams.·   Client Communications:·       Co-ordinate content and develop monthly client newsletter, co-ordinate electronic mail outs to clients including newsletters and invitations and co-ordinate and assist with targeted communications to industry associations
Please apply for this position by submitting your text CV using InternSG.
